==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Acton
<hw>Ac"ton</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF.
<ets>aketon</ets>, <ets>auqueton</ets>, F. <ets>hoqueton</ets>, a
quilted jacket, fr. Sp. <ets>alcoton</ets>, <ets>algodon</ets>, cotton.
Cf. <er>Cotton</er>.]</ety> <def>A stuffed jacket worn under the mail,
or (later) a jacket plated with mail.</def> <altsp>[Spelled also
<asp>hacqueton</asp>.]</altsp> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Halliwell.
Sir W. Scott.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Actor</ent>⟦br⟧
